#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid "desktop"
msgstr "namizje"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid "workspace"
msgstr "delovni prostor"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid "This is a module to configure general workspace behavior."
msgstr "To je modul za konfiguracijo splošnega obnašanja delovnega prostora."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allow Plasma to show panel and widget tooltips"
msgstr "Dovoli Plasmi, da prikaže namige za plošče in gradnike"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is checked, tooltips are displayed hovering items in the "
"&plasma; panel or on the desktop."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost označena, se namigi orodij prikažejo nad lebdečimi elementi "
"v &plasma; pultu ali na namizju."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allow Plasma to show OSD popups for status changes"
msgstr "Dovoli Plasmi, da prikaže pojavna okna na zaslonu za spremembe stanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is checked, all Plasma widgets are allowed to show on-screen "
"display (OSD) popups for changes like volume and brightness level, or audio "
"device switching."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost odkljukana, lahko vsi pripomočki Plasma prikažejo pojavna "
"okna na zaslonu za spremembe, kot sta raven glasnosti in svetlosti ali "
"preklop zvočne naprave."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "Animation speed"
msgstr "Hitrost animacije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows you to set the speed of desktop effect animations from "
"<guilabel>Slow</guilabel> to <guilabel>Instant</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča nastavitev hitrosti animacij namiznih učinkov od <guilabel>počasi</"
"guilabel> do <guilabel>takojšnje</guilabel>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Clicking files or folders</guimenu><guimenuitem>Opens them</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Klikanje datotek ali map</guimenu><guimenuitem>Jih odpre</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is checked, then files and folders will be opened with a "
"single click of the <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> mouse button. To select "
"files and folders, you can <mousebutton>left</mousebutton>-click on their "
"selection markers, drag a selection rectangle around them, or <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<mousebutton>Left</mousebutton></keycombo>-click. "
"This is the default behavior, and it's designed to be consistent with what "
"you would expect when you click links in web browsers."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost označena, se datoteke in mape odprejo z enim klikom "
"<mousebutton>levega</mousebutton> miškinega gumba. Datoteke in mape lahko "
"izberete tako, da <mousebutton>levo</mousebutton> kliknete na njihove "
"označevalnike za izbor, povlečete pravokotnik izbora okoli njih ali "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<mousebutton>levo</mousebutton></keycombo> "
"kliknete. To je privzeto obnašanje, ki je zasnovano tako, da je skladno s "
"pričakovanji pri klikanju povezav v spletnih brskalnikih."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Clicking files or folders</guimenu><guimenuitem>Selects them</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Klikanje datotek ali map</guimenu><guimenuitem>jih izbere</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is checked, then files and folders must be double-clicked to "
"be opened, while a single click will select them. This is the behavior you "
"may know from other desktops or operating systems."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost označena, je treba datoteke in mape odpreti z dvojnim "
"klikom, medtem ko jih izberete z enim klikom. Takšno obnašanje morda poznate "
"iz drugih namizij ali operacijskih sistemov."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Clicking in scrollbar track</guimenu><guimenuitem>Scrolls one page "
"up and down</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Klikanje v tirnici pomikanja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Potegne eno "
"stran navzgor in navzdol</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the default setting. Left-click in scrollbar track moves scrollbar "
"by one page."
msgstr ""
"To je privzeta nastavitev. Z levim klikom na sled v drsni vrstici premaknete "
"drsno vrstico za eno stran."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Clicking in scrollbar track</guimenu><guimenuitem>Scrolls to the "
"clicked location</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Klikanje v tirnici pomikanja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pretakne na "
"kliknjeno mesto</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Turns on the behavior when the scroll handle position jumps right to the "
"position in the document where you have clicked. This is the behavior you "
"may know from other desktops or operating systems."
msgstr ""
"Vklopi obnašanje, ko položaj ročice za pomikanje preskoči na položaj v "
"dokumentu, na katerega ste kliknili. Takšno obnašanje morda poznate iz "
"drugih namizij ali operacijskih sistemov."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Middle Click</guimenu><guimenuitem>Paste selected text</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Srednji klik</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prilepi izbrano besedilo</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is checked, middle-clicking in a text field will paste from "
"the clipboard, just like you would with <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keysym>V</keysym></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost označena, se s sredinskim klikom v besedilno polje prilepi "
"iz odložišča, tako kot pri uporabi <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keysym>V</keysym></keycombo>."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tablet Mode"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid "In Tablet Mode, the virtual keyboard will appear when needed."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:99
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<guimenu>Touch Mode</guimenu><guimenuitem>Automatically enable as needed</"
#| "guimenuitem>"
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tablet Mode</guimenu><guimenuitem>Automatically enable as needed</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Način na dotik</guimenu><guimenuitem>Samodejno omogoči po potrebi</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:101
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If this option is selected, Touch Mode will be automatically activated "
#| "whenever the system detects a touchscreen but no mouse or touchpad. For "
#| "example: when a transformable laptop's keyboard is flipped around or "
#| "detached."
msgid ""
"If this option is selected, Tablet Mode will be automatically activated "
"whenever the system detects a touchscreen but no mouse or touchpad. For "
"example: when a transformable laptop's keyboard is flipped around or "
"detached."
msgstr ""
"Če je izbrana ta možnost, se bo način na dotik samodejno aktiviral, ko "
"sistem zazna zaslon na dotik, ne pa tudi miške ali sledilne ploščice. Na "
"primer: ko je tipkovnica prenosnika, ki ga je mogoče spremeniti, obrnjena "
"ali odstranjena."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:108
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<guimenu>Touch Mode</guimenu><guimenuitem>Always enabled</guimenuitem>"
msgid "<guimenu>Tablet Mode</guimenu><guimenuitem>Always enabled</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Način na dotik</guimenu><guimenuitem>Vedno omogočeno</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:110
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If this option is selected, Touch Mode will always be enabled. Use this "
#| "option if you use &plasma; primarily with a touchscreen, or prefer larger "
#| "click targets for other reasons."
msgid ""
"If this option is selected, Tablet Mode will always be enabled. Use this "
"option if you use &plasma; primarily with a touchscreen."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete to možnost, bo način na dotik vedno omogočen. To možnost "
"uporabite, če uporabljate &plasma; predvsem z zaslonom na dotik ali imate "
"raje večje cilje klikov iz drugih razlogov."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:115
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "<guimenu>Touch Mode</guimenu><guimenuitem>Never enabled</guimenuitem>"
msgid "<guimenu>Tablet Mode</guimenu><guimenuitem>Never enabled</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Način na dotik</guimenu><guimenuitem>Nikoli omogočeno</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:117
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If this option is selected, Touch Mode will always be disabled. Use this "
#| "option if you don't need Touch Mode on your device."
msgid ""
"If this option is selected, Tablet Mode will always be disabled. Use this "
"option if you don't need Tablet Mode on your device."
msgstr ""
"Če izberete to možnost, bo način na dotik vedno onemogočen. Uporabite to "
"možnost, če na napravi ne potrebujete načina na dotik."

